<F P=100> NATIONAL AFFAIRS </F>
<F P=101> Political &amp; Social </F>
<H3> <TI>   Former NPC Vice Chairman Liu Ningyi Dies </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  OW1702133494 Beijing XINHUA in English 1313 GMT 17 Feb 94 </F>
<F P=103> OW1702133494 </F>
<F P=104>  Beijing XINHUA </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> English </F>
Article Type:BFN 

  [Text] Beijing, February 17 (XINHUA) -- Liu Ningyi, former 
vice-chairman of the Standing Committee of the Third National 
People's Congress, died of illness here on February 15 at the 
age of 87. 
  Liu Ningyi was an outstanding member of the Communist Party 
of China, a proletarian revolutionary and an outstanding leader 
of the workers' movement. 

</TEXT>

</DOC>

