investment and development of its economic reform, as well as 
his ideas about Sino-Slovak economic cooperation. 
  On the basis of equality and mutual benefit, Slovakia is 
ready to enhance economic and trade cooperative relations with 
China, he said. He hoped that more Chinese businessmen will go 
to Slovakia. 
  Some 30 representatives from China's large corporations and 
nearly 20 Slovak entrepreneurs attended the seminar and 
conducted business talks. 

